jodd.util.function

Interface Maybe<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Maybe.Just

    public interface Maybe<T>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Slightly better Maybe monad. It does not have a get(), but it has or() :). Slightly better implementation of Optional, as there are no IF blocks all over the class.
